ARMOR OF ITHAN: 30 MDC magical force field

Syntax: cast armor of ithan
        cast armorofithan
        cast ithan

DETAILS
  PPE Cost: 10
  Level:    3
  Duration: 5 minutes (300 seconds)
  Range:    Self

Creates a shimmering magical force field around the caster that absorbs
up to 30 MDC of damage before dissipating. The field does not stack with
itself: casting it again while already active has no effect.

When the field is depleted or expires, you receive a message.

Casters who know this spell: Ley Line Walker, Ley Line Rifter, Mystic,
Techno-Wizard, and most dragon races.

